what is angular ?

angular is a js framework which allows to creat reactive single page aplication

javascript schimba tot timpul acelasi html de x ori

js changes the domain

js schimba html

angular se schimba undeva la 6 luni. are mai multe variante. dar nu e musai un detaliu important

angular foloseste node.js ca sa isi faca background-ul fain
el folostes npm dependency node package manager

dependinte sunt framework-ul in sine

pentru a instala framework-ul:
npm install -g @angular/cli@latest

PENTRU A INITIA UN PROIECT
cd (change directory) + copy de la adress as text al folderului unde vrei angular + npm init @angular (nume proiect)

A command-line interface (CLI) is a text-based user interface (UI) used to run programs, manage computer files and interact with the computer.
Command-line interfaces are also called command-line user interfaces, console user interfaces and character user interfaces.
